    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, meticulously preserved by a single owner and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections, complemented by spotless alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, featuring supple leather upholstery with no signs of wear and a dashboard that still retains its original factory luster. Every service milestone has been documented through the authorized dealership, ensuring the mechanical performance is as smooth and responsive as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle without the new-car depreciation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
