    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m listing my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total showstopper. This beauty has been pampered since day one and looks like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single blemish to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. If you\u2019ve been looking for perfection, you just found it. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to be obsessed! \u2728",
