    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, with the double VANOS system meticulously serviced for optimal variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, transmitting torque to a factory limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed OEM specifications, and the rod bearings have been proactively replaced. The suspension geometry remains true, featuring refreshed bushings and dampers that maintain the chassis's legendary balance. Finished in pristine original paint with a flawless interior, this vehicle is mechanically turn-key and aesthetically museum-grade.",
